# 📘 PDF Chat Assistant

An AI-powered web app that lets you upload a PDF, preview it, and ask questions about its content. Built with React (frontend), Express.js (backend), MySQL (database), and OpenAI GPT (AI Q&A).

---

## ⚙️ Features

- 📤 Upload a PDF document
- 🖼️ Preview the PDF beside the chat
- 💬 Ask questions related to the PDF
- 🤖 Get AI-generated answers using OpenAI

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React, React Bootstrap, react-pdf
- **Backend:** Express.js, pdf-parse, OpenAI SDK
- **Database:** MongoDb
- **AI:** OpenAI GPT-4

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### 📦 Prerequisites

- Node.js (v18+)
- Mongo
- An OpenAI API Key ([get one here](https://platform.openai.com/account/api-keys))

---

## 🔧 Installation

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/pdf-chat-assistant.git
cd pdf-chat-assistant

## .env
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
MONGO_URL=your_mongo_url
